Package: quarto.website.intro
Title: Creating a Personal Website (Using Quarto)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hao",
           family = "Ye",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "haoye@ufl.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8630-1458"))
Description: Quarto is a new and versatile tool for writing content in markdown and publishing to a multitude of formats. This workshop will operate as a _Getting Started_ guide for using Quarto to create a personal website. Along the way, attendees will learn about other uses of Quarto and using GitHub Actions for continuous deployment.
